{"tid":626930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔相信愛情","createTime":"2018-04-12T13:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T15:53:51.000Z","uid":152109,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9dd1ae89fd2791b672306f752dfe25e45ea688f","tid":626930,"uid":152109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"係咪我廢，只係父母關係唔好<br />\n已經唔想再鋪佢地後塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢覺得自己係學校入面同人好唔同好異類e.g 相比人係好摺好內向<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日心入面都有條刺同好多個理由比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;&gt;&gt;根本唔需要拍拖結婚生仔<br />\nP.S 大家價值觀都唔同點解結婚後生埋自己先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔離婚又唔坐底解決⋯⋯係咪想等奇蹟兩個關係無拉拉會好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n#無開始就無結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424cbde8857bb408d7ea87cec463cbb22e158bf5","tid":626930,"uid":154986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"巴定絲"},{"pid":"3721e62145be0ee7983115a750a0812ac064769c","tid":626930,"uid":152109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"424cbde8857bb408d7ea87cec463cbb22e158bf5","tid":626930,"uid":154986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"巴定絲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"有分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30061147fb212aa82f0751f8119d753cb2657877","tid":626930,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dbce6246e0189708c6002d851aefa4166540ee4","tid":626930,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"我信<br />\n因為我好愛一個人<br />\n自己知道咩係愛就夠"},{"pid":"40debfae9c282fac9ea6f7317a8802be706e398f","tid":626930,"uid":154986,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"q